Copy the parent  directory to /usr/src/rt5572sta-2.6.1.3
(name is important)
Then as root run:
dkms add -m rt5572sta -v 2.6.1.3
dkms build -m rt5572sta -v 2.6.1.3
dkms install -m rt5572sta -v 2.6.1.3
dkms mkdeb -m rt5572sta -v 2.6.1.3

The deb file will be at /var/lib/dkms/rt5572sta/2.6.1.3/deb


(reference https://wiki.kubuntu.org/Kernel/Dev/DKMSPackaging)
